        Visits an executable type.

        If this method adds annotations to the type of method parameters, then GenericAnnotatedTypeFactory.addComputedTypeAnnotations(Element, AnnotatedTypeMirror) should be overridden and the same annotations added to the type of elements with kind ElementKind.PARAMETER. Likewise for return types.
